plyTime":"2017-08-08T11:59:42.000Z","msg":"已經唔記得係邊一間公司 小食餐有日式冷麵食<br />\n作為窮撚既我第一次食冷麵覺得好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5890e60d0726cf71645e9db2e6e6655c203eb973","tid":351690,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>帆船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我中學最後一年係呢間，對我黎講唯一好處係有得添飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕對同意, 呢間係我覺得最不濟既飯商</blockquote><br />\n見到個飯盒都唔開胃"}]}